title: Greenscreen
content:
Greenscreen 

Kort fortalt, på engelsk...

A green screen is a large green backdrop placed in the background of a shot to allow for digital effects later. In Post-Production, the special effects department will edit the background from green to… anything they want with CGI (computer-generated imagery) or background footage called "plates." The screen can take up the entire background or just a portion of it, depending on what needs to be replaced.

title: imageviewersus_main.lua
content:
local component = require("component")
local gpu = component.gpu

local sX, sY = gpu.getResolution()

-- Input from user
-- Get filenames


local filenames = {}
local currentFilename = ""

local resolution = {}
resolution.x = 0
resolution.y = 0
local duration = 0

print([[
    
    ImageViewersus
    
    Enter filenames including file extension: "example.sif" (without quotes)
    After each filename press enter to proceed
    Afteer you selected all filenames, type: "end" (without quotes)
    
    ]])

while currentFilename ~= "end" do
    currentFilename = io.read()
    if currentFilename ~= nil and currentFilename ~= "end" and currentFilename ~= "" then
        table.insert(filenames, currentFilename)
    end
end


print("\nEnter how long each image will play:\n")

duration = tonumber(io.read())

print("\nEnter resolution of image (max 80x50)\nExample: \"80x50\" without quotes\n")

local resolutionString = io.read()
local resolutionGmatch = resolutionString:gmatch("([^x]+)x?")

resolution.x = tonumber(resolutionGmatch())
resolution.y = tonumber(resolutionGmatch())
print(resolution.x, resolution.y)

print("\nStarting...\n")
os.sleep(1)


-- Loading files


local contents = {}

for i = 1, #filenames, 1 do
    table.insert(contents, io.open(filenames[i], "r"):read())
end


-- Converting data
-- Here's string data (for example: 000000) converts to number data (0)


local images = {}

for i, content in ipairs(contents) do
    local shiftY = 0 -- row/collumn i dont know. after adder it will be 1 as should
    local shiftX = resolution.x+1 -- basically it means 0
    
    table.insert(images, {})

    for stringColor in string.gmatch(content, "......") do
        if shiftX > resolution.x then -- row adder
    		table.insert(images[i], {})
        	shiftY = shiftY + 1
        	shiftX = 1
    	end
        
    	local color = tonumber("0x"..stringColor)
        table.insert(images[i][shiftY], color)
        shiftX = shiftX + 1
    end
end


-- Drawing images


gpu.setForeground(0x000000)
gpu.setBackground(0x000000)
gpu.setResolution(resolution.x*2, resolution.y)
gpu.fill(1, 1, sX, sY, " ")

while true do
    for i, image in ipairs(images) do
        for y, row in ipairs(image) do
            for x, col in ipairs(row) do
                gpu.setForeground(col)
                gpu.setBackground(col)
                gpu.set(x*2-1, y, "  ")
            end
        end
        os.sleep(duration)
    end
end

gpu.setForeground(0xFFFFFF)
gpu.setBackground(0x000000)
gpu.setResolution(160, 50)
gpu.fill(1, 1, 160, 50, " ")

--Tutte le coordinate sono relative alla posizione di partenza
local direction = 0 -- 0 = nord, 1 = east, 2 = sud, 3 = ovest
local offset_x = 0
local offset_y = 0
local offset_z = 0

function return_to_start()
    local action = true
    reposition_turtple()
    for _ = offset_z, 0, 1 do
        action = turtle.up()
    end
    return action
end

function reposition_turtple()
    while direction ~= 3 do
        rotate_right()
    end
    for _ = offset_x, 0, -1 do
        increment_position()
    end
    while direction ~= 2 do
        rotate_left()
    end
    for _ = offset_y, 0, -1 do
        increment_position()
    end
    while direction ~= 0 do
        rotate_left()
    end
end

function rotate_right()
    turtle.turnRight()
    direction = direction + 1
    if direction == 4 then
        direction = 0
    end
end

function rotate_left()
    turtle.turnLeft()
    direction = direction - 1
    if direction == -1 then
        direction = 3
    end
    direction = math.abs(direction)
    if direction == 4 then
        direction = 0
    end
end

function increment_position()
    local action = true
    action = turtle.forward()
    if not action then return false end
    if direction == 0 then
        offset_y = offset_y+1
    elseif direction == 1 then
        offset_x = offset_x+1
    elseif direction == 2 then
        offset_y = offset_y-1
    elseif direction == 3 then
        offset_x = offset_x-1
    end
    return action
end

turtle.digDown()
while true do
    local success = true
    local res = true

    for _ = 1, 15, 1 do
        res = increment_position()
        if success and not res then success = false end
        turtle.digDown()
    end

    for _ = 1, 7, 1 do
        rotate_right()
        res = increment_position()
        if success and not res then success = false end
        turtle.digDown()
        rotate_right()

        for _ = 1, 15, 1 do
            res = increment_position()
            if success and not res then success = false end
            turtle.digDown()
        end

        rotate_left()
        res = increment_position()
        if success and not res then success = false end
        turtle.digDown()
        rotate_left()

        for _ = 1, 15, 1 do
            res = increment_position()
            if success and not res then success = false end
            turtle.digDown()
        end
    end

    rotate_right()
    res = increment_position()
    if success and not res then success = false end
    turtle.digDown()
    rotate_right()

    for _ = 1, 15, 1 do
        res = increment_position()
        if success and not res then success = false end
        turtle.digDown()
    end

    turtle.down()
    offset_z = offset_z-1
    if not success then
        turtle.up()
        offset_z = offset_y+1
        break
    end
    reposition_turtple()
end
return_to_start()

-- "Visual trait" variables
local aoeColor = BrickColor.new("Dirt brown")
local aoeStartTrans = 0.5
local aoeStartSize = Vector3.new(45, 1.5, 45)
local aoeEndSize = Vector3.new(55, 3, 55)

-- "Mechanical trait" variables
local DMG = 100
local RADIUS = 40

local TweenService = game:GetService("TweenService")
local RunService = game:GetService("RunService")
local DamageService = require(game.ServerScriptService:WaitForChild("Libraries"):WaitForChild("DamageService"))

-- Attack script
function Use(...)
	local args = {...}
	local root = args[1].Character.Torso
	local humanoid = args[1].Character.Humanoid
	local plrAtt = Instance.new("Attachment", root)
	

	local aligner = Instance.new("Part")
	local alignerAtt = Instance.new("Attachment", aligner)
	aligner.CanCollide, aligner.Anchored, aligner.Transparency, aligner.CFrame =
		false, true, 1, root.CFrame*CFrame.Angles(0, math.rad(90), 0)
	aligner.Parent = workspace
	local plrAlignO = Instance.new("AlignOrientation")
	plrAlignO.Attachment0, plrAlignO.Attachment1, plrAlignO.RigidityEnabled =
		plrAtt, alignerAtt, true
	plrAlignO.Parent = root
	local plrBodyV = Instance.new("BodyVelocity")
	plrBodyV.MaxForce, plrBodyV.Velocity =
		Vector3.new(math.huge, math.huge, math.huge), Vector3.zero
	plrBodyV.Parent = root
	
	
	task.wait(0.12)
	local aoe = Instance.new("Part")
	aoe.Material, aoe.Anchored, aoe.CanCollide, aoe.CFrame, aoe.BrickColor, aoe.Transparency, aoe.Size =
		"SmoothPlastic", true, false, root.CFrame, aoeColor, aoeStartTrans, aoeStartSize
	local OnHeartbeat OnHeartbeat = RunService.Heartbeat:Connect(function() aoe.CFrame = root.CFrame end)
	-- AlignOrientation and AlignPosition proved incredibly strange-looking for AoE movement, so I opted for this approach.
	aoe.Parent = workspace
	DamageService:RegisterRangeDamage(args[1], RADIUS, DMG)
	aligner.CFrame *= CFrame.Angles(0, math.rad(-90), 0)
	plrBodyV.Velocity = Vector3.new(0, -3, 0)
	
	
	local SizeMod = TweenService:Create(aoe, TweenInfo.new(3.7, Enum.EasingStyle.Quint), {Size = aoeEndSize, Transparency = 1})
	SizeMod.Completed:Connect(function() aoe:Destroy() plrAtt:Destroy() OnHeartbeat:Disconnect() end)
	SizeMod:Play()
	task.wait(0.05)
	plrAlignO:Destroy() aligner:Destroy() plrBodyV:Destroy()
end

return Use

-- This code was written by Squeezemeister.


local function FindHittablePlayers()
	for i, Player in pairs(game.Players:GetChildren()) do
		if Player.Character ~= nil and Player.Character:FindFirstChild("Torso") and (Player.Character.Torso.Position - Model.Torso.Position).Magnitude <= 15 then
			return true
		end
	end
end

coroutine.wrap(function()
	while Model:FindFirstChild("SLP") do
		task.wait(5)

		local found = FindHittablePlayers()  -- don't make a table OR ELSE! (that's why its false)
		if found then
			local warning = game.ServerStorage.Items["ANGRY!"]:Clone()
			warning.CanCollide, warning.Anchored, warning.Massless, warning.CFrame =
				false, false, true, Model.Torso.CFrame*CFrame.new(-0.5, -0.5, 1)*CFrame.Angles(0, 0, math.rad(15))
			local weld = Instance.new("Weld")
			weld.Part0, weld.Part1, weld.C0 = warning, Model.Torso, CFrame.new(-0.5, -0.5, 1)
			weld.Parent = warning
			warning.Parent = workspace

			task.wait(0.5)  -- warning time
			warning:Destroy()

			local inner = Instance.new("Part")
			inner.CanCollide, inner.Massless, inner.CFrame = false, true, Model.Torso.CFrame
			inner.Material = "Neon"
			inner.BrickColor = BrickColor.new("Really black")
			inner.Size = Vector3.new(5, 5, 5)
			inner.Transparency = 0.5

			local outer = Instance.new("Part")
			outer.CanCollide, outer.Massless, outer.CFrame = false, true, Model.Torso.CFrame
			outer.Material = "Neon"
			outer.BrickColor = BrickColor.new("Dark indigo")
			outer.Size = Vector3.new(9, 9, 9)
			outer.Transparency = 0.8

			local light = Instance.new("PointLight")
			light.Enabled, light.Shadows = true, false
			light.Brightness, light.Range = 5, 10
			light.Color = Color3.new(0, 0, 0.498039)

			weld = Instance.new("Weld")
			weld.Part0, weld.Part1 = inner, Model.Torso
			weld.Parent = inner
			weld = Instance.new("Weld")
			weld.Part0, weld.Part1 = outer, Model.Torso
			weld.Parent = outer

			game:GetService("Debris"):AddItem(inner, 2)
			game:GetService("Debris"):AddItem(outer, 2)
			light.Parent = outer
			inner.Parent, outer.Parent = workspace, workspace

			for i, Player in pairs(game.Players:GetChildren()) do
				if Player.Character ~= nil and Player.Character:FindFirstChild("Torso") and (Player.Character.Torso.Position - Model.Torso.Position).Magnitude <= 15 then
					DamageMod:RegisterDamage(Model, Player, CLOSEDAMAGE)
					-- Below is the code for pushing.
						--[[
						local bv = Instance.new("BodyVelocity")
						bv.MaxForce, bv.Velocity = Vector3.new(math.huge, math.huge, math.huge), Model.Torso.CFrame.LookVector * 50
						game:GetService("Debris"):AddItem(bv, 0.5)
						bv.Parent = Player.Character.Torso
						]]
				end
			end
		end
	end
end)()

# Emoji Detector
# https://judge.softuni.org/Contests/Practice/Index/2302#1

import re


def find_coolest_emojis(emojis, coolness):
    cool_emojis = []
    emoji_coolness = 0

    for emoji in emojis:
        for char in emoji[2:-2]:
            emoji_coolness += ord(char)
        if emoji_coolness > coolness:
            cool_emojis.append(emoji)
            # emoji_coolness = 0 Това ти е грешката, тряба всеки път при изчисления да зануляваш, 
            # което означава да го мръднеш малко на дясно за да хваща всеки случай
        emoji_coolness = 0
    return cool_emojis


text = input()
#  Патърна ти беше грешен и не мачавше праилно, променил съм го
object_pattern = r"(::|\*\*)([A-Z][a-z]{2,})\1"
digit_pattern = r"\d"
matched_emojis = []
cool_threshold = 1
matches = 0

extracted_emojis = re.finditer(object_pattern, text)
extracted_digits = re.findall(digit_pattern, text)

for current_digit in extracted_digits:
    cool_threshold = cool_threshold * int(current_digit)

for current in extracted_emojis:
    matched_emojis.append("".join(current.group(1, 2, 1)))
    matches += 1

result = find_coolest_emojis(matched_emojis, cool_threshold)

print(f"Cool threshold: {cool_threshold}")
print(f"{matches} emojis found in the text. The cool ones are:")
for cool_emoji in result:
    print(cool_emoji)

local component = require("component")
local gpu = component.gpu


-- Input from user
-- Get filenames


local filenames = {}
local currentFilename = ""

local resolution = {}
resolution.x = 0
resolution.y = 0
local duration = 0

print([[
    
    ImageViewersus
    
    Enter filenames including file extension: "example.sif" (without quotes)
    After each filename press enter to proceed
    Afteer you selected all filenames, type: "end" (without quotes)
    
    ]])

while currentFilename ~= "end" do
    currentFilename = io.read()
    if currentFilename ~= nil and currentFilename ~= "end" and currentFilename ~= "" then
        table.insert(filenames, currentFilename)
    end
end


print("\nEnter how long each image will play:\n")

duration = tonumber(io.read())

print("\nEnter resolution of image (max 80x50)\nExample: \"80x50\" without quotes\n")

local resolutionString = io.read()
local resolutionGmatch = resolutionString:gmatch("([^x]+)x?")

resolution.x = tonumber(resolutionGmatch())
resolution.y = tonumber(resolutionGmatch())
print(resolution.x, resolution.y)

print("\nStarting...\n")
os.sleep(1)


-- Loading files


local contents = {}

for i = 1, #filenames, 1 do
    table.insert(contents, io.open(filenames[i], "r"):read())
end


-- Converting data
-- Here's string data (for example: 000000) converts to number data (0)


local images = {}


for i, content in ipairs(contents) do
    local shift = 0 -- row/collumn i dont know. after adder it will be 1 as should
    local localY = resolution.x+1 -- basically it means 0
    
    table.insert(images, {})

    for stringColor in string.gmatch(content, "......") do
        if localY > resolution.x then -- row adder
    		table.insert(images[i], {})
        	shift = shift + 1
        	localY = 1
    	end
        
    	local color = tonumber("0x"..stringColor)
        table.insert(images[i][shift], color)
        localY = localY + 1
    end
end


-- Drawing images


gpu.setForeground(0x000000)
gpu.setBackground(0x000000)
gpu.setResolution(resolution.x*2, resolution.y)
gpu.fill(1, 1, resolution.x*2, resolution.y, " ")

for i, image in ipairs(images) do
    for y, row in ipairs(image) do
        for x, col in ipairs(row) do
            gpu.setForeground(col)
            gpu.setBackground(col)
            gpu.set(x*2-1, y, "  ")
        end
    end
    os.sleep(duration)
end

gpu.setForeground(0xFFFFFF)
gpu.setBackground(0x000000)
gpu.setResolution(160, 50)
gpu.fill(1, 1, 160, 50, " ")

content:
# Xiaomi Mi Scale 2
# Mit ESP-12F und HX711
# https://docs.ai-thinker.com/_media/esp8266/docs/esp-12f_product_specification_en.pdf
# https://esp8266-server.de/waage.html

# GPIO0: BOOT-Taster
# GPIO2: Onboard-LED
# GPIO4: Kontakt für KEEPALIVE
# GPIO12: HX711 DOUT
# GPIO14: HX711 CLK
# GPIO16: RST für Deep Sleep

# Kabelfarben:
# Blau: TxD
# Grün: RxD
# Gelb: GPIO4
# Orange: GPIO0

substitutions:
  devicename: te-gaswaage
  friendly_devicename: Te Gaswaage

esphome:
  name: ${devicename}
  friendly_name: "${friendly_devicename}"
  on_boot:
    - priority: -300
      then:
        - script.execute: id_autostart
      
esp8266:
  board: esp12e
  framework:
    version: recommended
  restore_from_flash: true

# Enable logging
#logger:

# Enable Home Assistant API
api:

ota:
  password: !secret api_ota_password

wifi:
  ssid: !secret wifi_ssid
  password: !secret wifi_password
  fast_connect: true
  power_save_mode: light
  
  # Enable fallback hotspot (captive portal) in case wifi connection fails
  ap:
    ssid: "${friendly_devicename} AP"
    password: !secret ap_wifi_password

#web_server:
#  port: 80

captive_portal:

# Battery powered device
deep_sleep:
  run_duration: 1min
  sleep_duration: 3h
  id: id_deep_sleep
  
globals:

  - id: id_update_count
    type: int
    restore_value: no
    initial_value: '0'

  - id: id_tara_weight
    type: float
    restore_value: yes
    initial_value: '0'

# Time sync
time:
  - platform: homeassistant
    id: id_time
    on_time_sync:
      then:
        - delay: 3s
        - wait_until:
            lambda: return (id(id_update_count) >= 4);
        - if:
            condition:
              binary_sensor.is_on: id_keepalive
            then:
              - deep_sleep.prevent: id_deep_sleep
              - script.execute: id_update_sensors
            else:
              - deep_sleep.enter: id_deep_sleep

# Onboard LED
#status_led:
#  pin:
#    number: GPIO2
#    inverted: true

button:
  
  # Restart button
  - platform: restart
    name: "Neustart"
  
  # Restart button (safe mode)  
  - platform: safe_mode
    name: "Neustart (abgesicherter Modus)"
    
  # Tara button
  - platform: template
    name: "Tara"
    icon: mdi:scale-balance    
    on_press:
      - lambda: id(id_tara_weight) = id(id_gross_weight).state;

binary_sensor:

  # Connection Status sensor
  - platform: status
    name: "Status"
    id: id_status

  # Keepalive (Software)
  - platform: homeassistant
    name: "Keepalive (Software)"
    entity_id: input_boolean.te_gaswaage_keepalive_software
    internal: true
    id: id_keepalive_software
    
  # Keepalive (Hardware)
  - platform: gpio
    pin:
      number: GPIO4
      mode:
        input: true
        pullup: true
      inverted: true
    name: "Online bleiben (Hardware)"
    internal: true
    id: id_keepalive_hardware
    entity_category: diagnostic

  # Keepalive (Hard- und Software)
  - platform: template
    name: "Online bleiben"
    id: id_keepalive
    lambda: return (id(id_keepalive_hardware).state || id(id_keepalive_software).state);
    entity_category: diagnostic
    icon: mdi:wifi-check

  # Battery Level
  # https://data.energizer.com/pdfs/l92.pdf
  # https://docs.ai-thinker.com/_media/esp8266/docs/esp-12f_product_specification_en.pdf
  - platform: template
    name: "Batteriestand"
    id: id_lowbat
    device_class: battery
    entity_category: diagnostic
    lambda: return (id(id_voltage).state < 2.8);

sensor:
  
  # WiFi Signal sensor
  - platform: wifi_signal
    name: "WiFi Signalstärke"
    id: id_wifi
    update_interval: never
    on_value:
      lambda: id(id_update_count)++;

  # Battery voltage sensor
  - platform: adc
    pin: VCC
    name: "Batteriespannung"
    id: id_voltage
    update_interval: never
    on_value:
      lambda: id(id_update_count)++;
    filters:
      - calibrate_linear:
          - 2.78027 -> 2.690
          - 3.42188 -> 3.311

  # Scale
  - platform: hx711
    name: "Bruttogewicht"
    id: id_gross_weight
    dout_pin: GPIO12
    clk_pin: GPIO14
    gain: 128
    update_interval: never
    on_value:
      lambda: id(id_update_count)++;
    filters:
      - calibrate_linear:
          - 554600 -> 0000
          - 581200 -> 1026
    unit_of_measurement: g
    internal: true

  # Net Weight calculation (Tara)
  - platform: template
    name: "Gewicht"
    id: id_weight
    lambda: return (id(id_gross_weight).state - id(id_tara_weight));
    icon: mdi:scale
    unit_of_measurement: g
    update_interval: never
    accuracy_decimals: 0
    on_value:
      lambda: id(id_update_count)++;
    
script:

  # started after finished booting
  - id: id_autostart
    then:
      - lambda: |-
          id(id_update_count) = 0;
          id(id_voltage).update();
          id(id_gross_weight).update();
          id(id_weight).update();
          id(id_wifi).update();

  # started after time sync (== API connection established)
  # only if keepalive enabled (debugging, OTA etc)
  - id: id_update_sensors
    mode: single
    then:
      - while:
          condition:
            binary_sensor.is_on: id_keepalive
          then:
            - lambda: |-
                id(id_voltage).update();
                id(id_gross_weight).update();
                id(id_weight).update();
                id(id_wifi).update();
            - delay: 1s
      - deep_sleep.enter: id_deep_sleep

title: Query para sacar productos con marca y submarca
content:
select DISTINCT productos.nombre AS nombre
    ,empresaProducto.precioVenta AS precioVenta
    ,productos.descripcionURL AS descripcionURL
    ,marcas.descripcion as marca
    ,subMarcas.descripcion AS submarca
    ,subMarcas.descripcionUrl AS submarcaUrl
    ,imagenProducto.url AS imagen
    ,empresaProducto.idEmpresa AS idEmpresa
    ,IFNULL(descuentos.descuento,0) AS descuento
    ,IFNULL(descuentos.idTipoDescuento,0) AS idTipoDescuento
from productos 
INNER JOIN empresaProducto
    ON empresaProducto.idProducto = productos.id
        AND productos.idEstadoProducto IN (1,2)
        AND empresaProducto.idEmpresa = 1
    AND empresaProducto.activo = 1
LEFT JOIN descuentos
    ON empresaProducto.id = descuentos.idEmpresaProducto
        AND descuentos.activo = 1
INNER JOIN imagenProducto 
    ON productos.id = imagenProducto.idProducto
    AND imagenProducto.numero = 1
    AND imagenProducto.activo = 1
INNER JOIN marcaProducto
    ON empresaProducto.idProducto = marcaProducto.idProducto
    AND marcaProducto.activo = 1
INNER JOIN marcas
    ON marcaProducto.idMarca = marcas.id
LEFT JOIN subMarcaProducto
    ON productos.id = subMarcaProducto.idProducto
LEFT JOIN subMarcas
    ON subMarcaProducto.idSubMarca = subMarcas.id

with 
users as (select --получаем список клиентов из 37 теста и убираем фрод согласно условию
			atu.user_id 
			, atu.test_group
			, u.currency 
		  from dwh_mb_dedup.ab_test_user atu 
		  left join bi.users u on atu.user_id = u.user_id 
		  where atu.ab_test_id = 37
		  and u.frozen + u.locked + u.limited = 0 --убираем заблоченых
		  and (atu.user_id not in (select distinct external_id::int as `user_id`  from dwh_refp_dedup.referral r where created_at > '2023-06-21') --убираем рефералов
		  or atu.user_id not in	(select distinct user_id from bi.bonuses where nominal_bonus * 10 = exchange_bonus_amount)) --убираем тех у кого отыгрыш = 10номиналов бонуса
		  ),
cte_0 as(select --получаем пользователей которые получили бонусы  и сколько
			user_id, 
			count(id) as `bonus_cnt`
		 from dwh_mbb_dedup.balance b2 
		 group by user_id),
cte_1 as (select --получаем кол-во ставок с реального счета, сумму ставок и ggr на 1 клиента
			user_id 
			, count(ac.amount_usd) as `amount_real_cnt`
			, sum(ac.amount_usd) as `amount_real_sum`
			, sum(ac.ggr_usd) as `ggr_real_sum`
		  from bi.all_coupons ac where origin not in ('mostbet', 'toto') --кроме спорта и тото
		  group by user_id, currency),
cte_2 as (select --получаем кол-во ставок с бонусного счета
			user_id 
			, count(o.amount) as `amount_bonus_cnt`
		  from dwh_mbb_dedup.bonus b
		  right join (select
						*
					  from dwh_mbb_dedup.operation
					  where created_at >= '2023-06-21'
					  and project_id = 1) o 
		  on b.balance_id = o.balance_id
		  where user_id != ''
		  and b.`type` like '%CASINO'
		  group by user_id),
cte_3 as (select --получаем кол-во отыгранных бонусов на 1 чел
			user_id
			, sum(exchange_bonus_amount_usd > 0.00001) as exchange_bonuses_cnt
		  from bi.bonuses b
		  where b.bonus_created >= '2023-06-21' 
	      and project_id = 1
		  group by user_id),
cte_4 as(select --получаем кол-во бонусов на 1 чел, в которые играли. Хотя бы 1 ставка на бонусные деньги в бонусном счету
			b.user_id as `user_id`
			, count(distinct b.balance_id) as `bonuses_used_cnt`
			from dwh_mbb_dedup.bonus b
			right join (select
							*
						from dwh_mbb_dedup.operation
						where created_at >= '2023-06-21'
						and project_id = 1) o 
			on b.balance_id = o.balance_id
			where b.user_id != ''
			and b.`type` like '%CASINO'
			group by b.user_id),
cte_5 as (select --получаем суммы денег выведеннные с бонусного счета и выданные на бонусный счет
		    user_id
		    , sum(exchange_bonus_amount_usd) as `exchange_bonus_amount_sum`
			, sum(cr.rate * b.nominal_bonus) as `nominal_bonus_sum`
			from (select
				bonus_created
				, currency
				, user_id
				, nominal_bonus
				, exchange_bonus_amount_usd
			from bi.bonuses
			where project_id = 1) b
			left join bi.currency_rates cr on b.currency = cr.currency_code and b.bonus_created = cr.`date`
			group by user_id),
cte_7 as (select --получаем кол-во бонусов кашбеков и по программе лояльности отыгранных в реал
			user_id
			, sum(if(b.`type` like '%LOSE_CASINO', 1, 0)) as `cashback_lose_cnt`
			, sum(if(b.`type` like '%EXCHANGE_CASINO', 1, 0)) as `cashback_exchange_cnt`
		  from dwh_mbb_dedup.bonus b
		  where project_id = 1
		  group by user_id)
select users.*
        , if(cte_1.amount_real_cnt > 0, 1, 0) as `amount_real_flag`
        , if(cte_1.amount_real_cnt > 0 or cte_2.amount_bonus_cnt >0, 1, 0) as `amount_real_or_bonus_flag`
        , if(cte_1.amount_real_cnt > 0 and cte_2.amount_bonus_cnt >0, 1, 0) as `amount_real_and_bonus_flag`
        , if(cte_2.amount_bonus_cnt >0, 1, 0) as amount_bonus_flag
--        , cte_0.bonus_cnt -- кто просто получил бонус
        , if(cte_0.bonus_cnt > 0, divide(cte_3.exchange_bonuses_cnt, cte_0.bonus_cnt), null) as `exchange_bonuses_cnt`
        , if(cte_0.bonus_cnt > 0, divide(cte_4.bonuses_used_cnt, cte_0.bonus_cnt), null) as `bonuses_used_cnt`
        , if(cte_0.bonus_cnt > 0, cte_5.exchange_bonus_amount_sum, null) as `loss1`
        , cte_5.exchange_bonus_amount_sum as `loss2`
        , if(cte_0.bonus_cnt > 0, cte_5.nominal_bonus_sum, null) as `nominal_bonus_sum`
        , if(cte_0.bonus_cnt > 0, divide(cte_5.exchange_bonus_amount_sum, cte_5.nominal_bonus_sum), null) as `win_rate`
        , if(cte_7.cashback_lose_cnt > 0, cte_7.cashback_lose_cnt, null) as `cashback_lose_cnt`
        , if(cte_7.cashback_exchange_cnt > 0, cte_7.cashback_exchange_cnt, null) as `cashback_exchange_cnt`
        , if(cte_2.amount_bonus_cnt > 0, cte_1.amount_real_sum, null) as `amount_bonus_sum` --Сумма ставок на человека, сделавшего хотя бы 1 ставку на бонусные деньги
        , if(cte_2.amount_bonus_cnt > 0, cte_1.ggr_real_sum, null) as `ggr_bonus_sum` --GGR на человека, сделавшего хотя бы 1 ставку на бонусные деньги
        , cte_1.amount_real_sum as `amount_real_sum` --Сумма ставок на человека
        , cte_1.ggr_real_sum as `ggr_real_sum` --GGR на человека
from users 
left join cte_0 on users.user_id = cte_0.user_id::UInt64

Sub TransferData()
    Dim mainSheet As Worksheet
    Dim destSheet As Worksheet
    Dim lastRow As Long
    Dim i As Long
    
    Set mainSheet = ThisWorkbook.Worksheets("Main")
    
    ' Loop through each district sheet and clear its data
    For Each destSheet In ThisWorkbook.Worksheets
        If destSheet.Name <> "Main" And destSheet.Name <> "Districts" Then
            destSheet.Cells.ClearContents
        End If
    Next destSheet
    
    lastRow = mainSheet.Cells(mainSheet.Rows.Count, "A").End(xlUp).Row
    
    ' Loop through the rows in the main sheet and transfer data to the respective district sheets
    For i = 2 To lastRow ' Assuming your data starts from row 2, change if necessary
        Dim district As String
        district = mainSheet.Cells(i, "E").Value ' Assuming the district column is column "E," change if necessary
        
        ' Find the respective district sheet and transfer the row data
        On Error Resume Next
        Set destSheet = ThisWorkbook.Worksheets(district)
        On Error GoTo 0
        
        ' If the district sheet is found, transfer the row data
        If Not destSheet Is Nothing Then
            lastRow = destSheet.Cells(destSheet.Rows.Count, "A").End(xlUp).Row
            destSheet.Rows(lastRow + 1).Value = mainSheet.Rows(i).Value
        End If
    Next i
End Sub

select
	cancellation.*,
	bank.bank_name,
	bank.product_name,
	card.name_type as card_type_name,
	terminal.terminal_name,
	terminal_type.terminal_type_name,
	station.station_name,
	registration.name as nama,
	registration.nik as nik,
	cancellation.user_id as petugas
from
	trx.t_trx_subs_card_cancellation cancellation
left join master.t_mtr_bank bank on
	bank.bank_code = cancellation.card_issuer
left join master.t_mtr_station station on
	cancellation.station_code = station.station_id
left join master.t_mtr_device_terminal terminal on
	terminal.terminal_code = cancellation.terminal_code
left join master.t_mtr_device_terminal_type terminal_type on
	terminal.terminal_type = terminal_type.terminal_type_code
left join master.t_mtr_subs_card_registration registration on
	registration.uid = cancellation.uid
	and registration.card_number = cancellation.card_number
	and registration.status = 1
left join master.t_mtr_subs_card_type card on
	card.subs_card_type_id = cancellation.card_type
where
	cancellation.status = 1
	and card.subs_card_type_id = '11'
	and (DATE(cancellation.created_on) between '2023-07-23' and '2023-07-27' )
